{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813765069,"sessionID":"ses_289437761ffeqHEX2p9ix6cHvm","part":{"id":"prt_d76bc95ec001s418rSo83gu0P2","messageID":"msg_d76bc8981001KpA57fnwEpQ3Wl","sessionID":"ses_289437761ffeqHEX2p9ix6cHvm","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_4de6dcef28944200b277ddd8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project thoroughly. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure - find the root directory and key folders\n2. Look for any existing tasks.md files or similar checklist patterns to follow the convention\n3. Examine the pkg/workloadmanager directory if it exists - what's already there?\n4. Look at other pkg/ modules to understand the patterns used (HTTP service frameworks, routing, middleware, etc.)\n5. Find any existing HTTP service implementations in the project to understand conventions (e.g., how routes are defined, middleware usage, server setup)\n6. Check for any design documents, specs, or AR (Architecture Record) files related to AR-004 or ST-3\n7. Look at go.mod to understand what HTTP frameworks/libraries are available\n8. Check for any existing test patterns in the project\n\nReturn ALL findings in detail including:\n- Full project structure (directory tree)\n- Contents of any relevant tasks.md or checklist files (full content)\n- Contents of pkg/workloadmanager (all files)\n- Examples of HTTP service patterns from other modules (file paths and key code snippets)\n- Any AR or design doc content\n- go.mod dependencies related to HTTP/web frameworks\n- Test file patterns and examples","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_289434f24fferWoxDvCS2bGvCC (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is my complete report:\n\n---\n\n## Complete AgentCube Project Exploration Report\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\n\n**Project Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z`\n\n**Module:** `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n\n**Full Directory Tree:**\n\n```\n.\n├── .sdd_prompt.md                          # SDD prompt for AR-004 design generation\n├── changes/                                # Architecture Record changes\n│   ├── AR-001/                             # CRD AgentRuntime type definition\n│   │   ├── design.md\n│   │   ├── proposal.md\n│   │   └── tasks.md\n│   ├── AR-002/                             # CRD CodeInterpreter type definition\n│   │   ├── design.md\n│   │   ├── proposal.md\n│   │   └── tasks.md\n│   ├── AR-003/                             # CRD shared types & constants\n│   │   ├── design.md\n│   │   ├── proposal.md\n│   │   └── tasks.md\n│   └── AR-004/                             # WorkloadManager HTTP service framework (TARGET)\n│       ├── delta-spec.md\n│       ├── design.md\n│       ├── proposal.md\n│       └── tasks.md\n├── ci-cd/\n│   └── design.md\n├── cli-toolkit/\n│   └── design.md\n├── code-execution/\n│   ├── design.md                           # PicoD design\n│   └── spec.md\n├── coverage.out                            # Test coverage output\n├── delta-spec.md                           # AR-004 Gherkin-style requirements (REQ-001 through REQ-006)\n├── deployment/\n│   ├── client-go.md                        # Generated client-go library reference\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── design.md                               # AR-003 design (shared types refactoring)\n├── go.mod                                  # Go module definition\n├── go.sum\n├── idle-cleanup/\n│   └── design.md\n├── integrations/\n│   └── design.md\n├── pkg/\n│   └── apis/\n│       └── runtime/\n│           └── v1alpha1/                   # CRD type definitions (AR-001/002/003)\n│               ├── agent_type.go\n│               ├── agent_type_test.go\n│               ├── codeinterpreter_types.go\n│               ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go\n│               ├── constants.go\n│               ├── constants_test.go\n│               ├── doc.go\n│               ├── groupversion_info.go\n│               ├── groupversion_info_test.go\n│               ├── shared_types.go\n│               ├── shared_types_test.go\n│               └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n├── project.md                              # Project context document\n├── python-sdk/\n│   └── design.md\n├── sandbox-orchestration/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── session-routing/\n│   ├── design.md                           # Router HTTP service (Gin-based)\n│   └── spec.md\n├── session-store/\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n├── test_spec.md\n└── testing/\n    └── agentcube_tdd_manifest.md           # TDD test contract\n```\n\n**Note:** `pkg/workloadmanager/` does **NOT** exist yet. It is the target of AR-004 and needs to be created.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Tasks.md Files and Checklist Convention\n\nAll tasks.md files follow a consistent convention located at `changes/AR-XXX/tasks.md`:\n\n**Template Pattern (from AR-004):**\n```markdown\n# AR-004 任务清单\n\n> **Stage**: ST-1 (Proposal)\n> **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n> **Language**: Go\n> **Size**: M\n\n---\n\n## T-001: <!-- TODO: 任务标题 -->\n\n- [ ] T-001.01\n\n**验收**: <!-- TODO: 验收标准 -->\n\n---\n\n## T-003: 全量验证门禁\n\n- [ ] T-003.01 `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n- [ ] T-003.02 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` 全部通过\n\n**验收**: 全部检查项通过，AR-004 可标记为完成\n```\n\n**Key conventions:**\n- Tasks numbered as `T-001`, `T-002`, etc.\n- Subtasks numbered as `T-001.01`, `T-001.02`, etc.\n- Each task has a header `## T-XXX: 任务标题`\n- Subtasks use markdown checkboxes `- [ ]`\n- Each task ends with `**验收**: 验收标准`\n- Final task is always \"全量验证门禁\" (full verification gate) with `go build` and `go test` checks\n- AR-001 has 14 tasks (199 lines), AR-002 has 15 tasks (180 lines), AR-003 has 5 tasks (61 lines), AR-004 has 3 tasks (31 lines, mostly TODOs)\n\n---\n\n### 3. pkg/workloadmanager Directory\n\n**Does NOT exist yet.** The AR-004 design.md specifies the intended structure:\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n├── server.go                    # Server struct, NewServer(), Run(), Shutdown()\n├── config.go                    # Config struct, defaults, env var reading\n├── routes.go                    # SetupRoutes(engine *gin.Engine, deps *Dependencies)\n├── handler/\n│   ├── health.go                # GET /healthz, GET /readyz\n│   ├── agent_runtime.go         # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n│   └── code_interpreter.go      # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n├── middleware/\n│   └── request_id.go            # X-Request-ID tracking middleware\n├── response/\n│   └── response.go              # JSON(), Error(), Created() response helpers\n├── server_test.go\n├── config_test.go\n├── routes_test.go\n├── handler/\n│   ├── health_test.go\n│   ├── agent_runtime_test.go\n│   └── code_interpreter_test.go\n└── response/\n    └── response_test.go\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Existing pkg/ Modules (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/)\n\n**All files:**\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `doc.go` | Package doc with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` and `+groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| `groupversion_info.go` | GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme, Kind constants, Resource() helper |\n| `shared_types.go` | ProtocolType, AuthModeType enums + TargetPort struct |\n| `constants.go` | Well-known annotation keys |\n| `agent_type.go` | AgentRuntime CRD (embeds corev1.PodSpec via SandboxTemplate) |\n| `codeinterpreter_types.go` | CodeInterpreter CRD (flat fields via CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate) |\n| `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Auto-generated DeepCopy methods |\n\n**Key patterns:**\n- All types use `metav1.TypeMeta` + `metav1.ObjectMeta` embedding for CRD root types\n- Kubebuilder markers: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`\n- JSON tags use camelCase\n- Scheme registration via `init()` calling `SchemeBuilder.Register()`\n- Package: `v1alpha1`, Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n\n---\n\n### 5. Existing HTTP Service Patterns\n\nThere are **no existing Go HTTP service implementations** in the `pkg/` directory. However, detailed design docs describe two HTTP services:\n\n#### A. Session Router (session-routing/design.md) -- Uses Gin\n\n**Server struct pattern:**\n```go\ntype Server struct {\n    config         *Config\n    engine         *gin.Engine\n    httpServer     *http.Server\n    sessionManager SessionManager\n    storeClient    store.Store\n    httpTransport  *http.Transport\n    jwtManager     *JWTManager\n}\n```\n\n**Gin setup pattern:**\n```go\ngin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)  // or DebugMode based on config\nengine := gin.New()\nengine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n```\n\n**Route registration pattern:**\n```go\n// Health endpoints (no middleware)\nengine.GET(\"/health/live\", handleHealthLive)\nengine.GET(\"/health/ready\", handleHealthReady)\n\n// API group with middleware\nv1 := engine.Group(\"/v1\")\nv1.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery(), concurrencyLimitMiddleware)\n{\n    v1.GET(\"/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path\", handleAgentInvoke)\n    v1.POST(\"/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path\", handleAgentInvoke)\n}\n```\n\n**HTTP server:**\n```go\nserver := &http.Server{\n    Addr:         fmt.Sprintf(\":%d\", config.Port),\n    Handler:      engine,\n    ReadTimeout:  30 * time.Second,\n    IdleTimeout:  90 * time.Second,\n}\n// Supports h2c/http2\n```\n\n#### B. PicoD (code-execution/design.md) -- Uses Gin\n\n**Gin setup pattern:**\n```go\ngin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)\nengine := gin.New()\nengine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n\napi := engine.Group(\"/api\")\napi.Use(authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n{\n    api.POST(\"/execute\", s.ExecuteHandler)\n    api.POST(\"/files\", s.UploadFileHandler)\n    api.GET(\"/files\", s.ListFilesHandler)\n    api.GET(\"/files/*path\", s.DownloadFileHandler)\n}\nengine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)\n```\n\n**HTTP server:**\n```go\nserver := &http.Server{\n    Addr:              fmt.Sprintf(\":%d\", s.config.Port),\n    Handler:           s.engine,\n    ReadHeaderTimeout: 10 * time.Second,\n}\nreturn server.ListenAndServe()\n```\n\n**Error response pattern (gin.H):**\n```go\n// Generic (400/500): {\"error\": string, \"code\": int}\n// Auth (401): {\"error\": string, \"code\": int, \"detail\": string}\n```\n\n**Health response:**\n```go\nc.JSON(http.StatusOK, gin.H{\n    \"status\":  \"ok\",\n    \"service\": \"PicoD\",\n    \"version\": \"0.0.1\",\n    \"uptime\":  time.Since(s.startTime).String(),\n})\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. AR-004 Design Document (Key Content)\n\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/design.md` (636 lines)\n\n**Key specifications:**\n\n**Route table:**\n| Method | Path | Handler |\n|--------|------|---------|\n| GET | `/healthz` | HealthzHandler |\n| GET | `/readyz` | ReadyzHandler |\n| POST | `/api/v1/agentruntimes` | CreateAgentRuntime |\n| GET | `/api/v1/agentruntimes` | ListAgentRuntimes |\n| GET | `/api/v1/agentruntimes/:name` | GetAgentRuntime |\n| PUT | `/api/v1/agentruntimes/:name` | UpdateAgentRuntime |\n| DELETE | `/api/v1/agentruntimes/:name` | DeleteAgentRuntime |\n| POST | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters` | CreateCodeInterpreter |\n| GET | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters` | ListCodeInterpreters |\n| GET | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters/:name` | GetCodeInterpreter |\n| PUT | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters/:name` | UpdateCodeInterpreter |\n| DELETE | `/api/v1/codeinterpreters/:name` | DeleteCodeInterpreter |\n\n**Middleware chain:**\n```\nRequest -> gin.Recovery() -> gin.Logger() -> RequestIDMiddleware -> Handler\n```\n\n**Config struct:**\n```go\ntype Config struct {\n    Port         int           // default 8080\n    KubeConfig   string        // empty = in-cluster\n    Namespace    string        // default \"default\"\n    ResyncPeriod time.Duration // default 30s\n}\n```\n\n**Server struct:**\n```go\ntype Server struct {\n    config  *Config\n    engine  *gin.Engine\n    httpSrv *http.Server\n    deps    *Dependencies\n}\n\ntype Dependencies struct {\n    Clientset   clientset.Interface\n    Informer    informers.SharedInformerFactory\n    ARLister    runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n    CILister    runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n}\n```\n\n**Error mapping:**\n```go\nfunc mapK8sError(err error) (int, int, string) {\n    // apierrors.IsNotFound -> 404, 40401\n    // apierrors.IsAlreadyExists -> 409, 40901\n    // apierrors.IsConflict -> 409, 40902\n    // apierrors.IsInvalid -> 400, 40003\n    // default -> 500, 50002\n}\n```\n\n**Implementation order (18 steps):** response -> config -> handlers -> middleware -> routes -> server\n\n---\n\n### 7. go.mod Dependencies\n\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod`\n\n```\nmodule github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\ngo 1.24.4\n\nrequire (\n    github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1\n    k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n    k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1\n    sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2\n)\n```\n\n**Notable: `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` is NOT yet in go.mod.** AR-004 requires adding it.\n\n**Indirect dependencies include:** go-logr/logr, gogo/protobuf, json-iterator, golang.org/x/net, golang.org/x/text, yaml.v2/yaml.v3, klog/v2, etc.\n\n---\n\n### 8. Test Patterns and Examples\n\n**Test files (5 existing):**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type_test.go` (235 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go` (654 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info_test.go` (80 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types_test.go` (77 lines)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants_test.go` (21 lines)\n\n**Test conventions:**\n- Package: same as source (`package v1alpha1`)\n- Framework: `github.com/stretchr/testify/assert`\n- Naming: `Test<Type><Scenario>` (e.g., `TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues`, `TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy`)\n- Patterns:\n  - **Default/zero-value tests**: Construct minimal struct, assert nil/empty fields\n  - **DeepCopy tests**: Construct full struct, call DeepCopy(), modify copy, assert original unchanged\n  - **Scheme registration tests**: Create `runtime.NewScheme()`, call `AddToScheme()`, verify `scheme.New(gvk)` returns correct type\n  - **Constant tests**: Direct equality assertions\n  - **All-fields tests**: Construct with all fields populated, assert each field value\n- Helper functions: `ptrInt32(i int32) *int32`, `parseQuantity(s string) resource.Quantity`\n\n**TDD Manifest requirements** (`testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md`):\n- T/C Ratio must be > 0.4 (every 100 lines of code needs at least 40 lines of tests)\n- Every source file must have a corresponding test file\n- Workload Manager tests require: Mock K8s Client, session conflict handling (409), Pod status sync, resource cleanup\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Key Findings\n\n1. **`pkg/workloadmanager/` does not exist** -- it must be created from scratch per AR-004\n2. **HTTP framework: Gin** is the chosen framework (already used by Router and PicoD per design docs, but not yet in go.mod)\n3. **No existing HTTP service code in pkg/** -- only CRD type definitions exist; HTTP patterns come from design docs\n4. **Test framework: testify/assert** with same-package test files\n5. **Tasks convention**: `changes/AR-004/tasks.md` with T-XXX numbering, checkbox subtasks, verification criteria, and a final \"全量验证门禁\" gate task\n6. **AR-004 design is comprehensive** -- 636 lines covering architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, testing strategy, and implementation steps\n7. **delta-spec.md** provides Gherkin-style requirements (REQ-001 through REQ-006)\n8. **client-go is pre-generated** with typed clients, informers, listers, and fake clients for both AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_289434f24fferWoxDvCS2bGvCC","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project","time":{"start":1775813570775,"end":1775813765066}}}}
