{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775813774533,"sessionID":"ses_289437761ffeqHEX2p9ix6cHvm","part":{"id":"prt_d76bfc83d001XwJKrHN8h2AnT2","messageID":"msg_d76bfa817001SCkCpDGOowuCSY","sessionID":"ses_289437761ffeqHEX2p9ix6cHvm","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_af1cb3d278b147c38bec85d5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-4 (Implementation)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: S\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## T-001: 创建 pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 目录结构\n11: \n12: - [ ] T-001.01 创建目录 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n13: - [ ] T-001.02 确认 `go.mod` 中 `k8s.io/api`、`k8s.io/apimachinery`、`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` 依赖版本正确（v0.34.1 / v0.22.2）\n14: \n15: **验收**: 目录存在；`go mod tidy` 无报错\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T-002: 创建 doc.go — 包声明与代码生成标记\n20: \n21: - [ ] T-002.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n22: - [ ] T-002.02 包含 `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` 标记\n23: - [ ] T-002.03 包含 `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` 标记\n24: - [ ] T-002.04 包名为 `v1alpha1`\n25: \n26: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## T-003: 创建 groupversion_info.go — GroupVersion 与 SchemeBuilder\n31: \n32: - [ ] T-003.01 定义 `GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n33: - [ ] T-003.02 定义 `SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}`\n34: - [ ] T-003.03 定义 `AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme`\n35: - [ ] T-003.04 导入 `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema`\n36: - [ ] T-003.05 导入 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme`\n37: \n38: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`GroupVersion.Group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`；`GroupVersion.Version == \"v1alpha1\"`\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## T-004: 创建 register.go — Kind 元数据与 Resource 辅助函数\n43: \n44: - [ ] T-004.01 定义 `AgentRuntimeKind = \"AgentRuntime\"`\n45: - [ ] T-004.02 定义 `AgentRuntimeListKind = \"AgentRuntimeList\"`\n46: - [ ] T-004.03 定义 `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")`\n47: - [ ] T-004.04 定义 `SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion`（别名，兼容 client-go 代码生成）\n48: - [ ] T-004.05 定义 `func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource` 返回 `GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)`\n49: - [ ] T-004.06 定义 CodeInterpreter Kind 元数据（`CodeInterpreterKind`、`CodeInterpreterGroupKind`、`CodeInterpreterListKind`、`CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind`）供后续 AR-002 使用\n50: \n51: **验收**: `Resource(\"agentruntimes\")` 返回 `{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\"}`\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## T-005: 创建 codeinterpreter_types.go — 共享类型定义\n56: \n57: - [ ] T-005.01 定义 `type ProtocolType string`\n58: - [ ] T-005.02 定义常量 `ProtocolTypeHTTP ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"` 和 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"`\n59: - [ ] T-005.03 定义 `type TargetPort struct`，字段：`PathPrefix string`、`Name string`、`Port uint32`、`Protocol ProtocolType`（带 `+kubebuilder:default=HTTP` 和 `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` 标记）\n60: - [ ] T-005.04 定义 `type AuthModeType string`\n61: - [ ] T-005.05 定义常量 `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"` 和 `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n62: - [ ] T-005.06 所有字段使用正确的 JSON tag（camelCase: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`）\n63: \n64: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`；`TargetPort` 结构体字段与 JSON tag 映射正确\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## T-006: 创建 agent_type.go — AgentRuntime 核心类型定义\n69: \n70: ### T-006.1: AgentRuntime 根类型\n71: \n72: - [ ] T-006.1.01 定义 `type AgentRuntime struct`，嵌入 `metav1.TypeMeta` 和 `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n73: - [ ] T-006.1.02 字段 `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec`（JSON tag: `spec`）\n74: - [ ] T-006.1.03 字段 `Status AgentRuntimeStatus`（JSON tag: `status,omitempty`）\n75: - [ ] T-006.1.04 添加标记 `+genclient`\n76: - [ ] T-006.1.05 添加标记 `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n77: - [ ] T-006.1.06 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n78: - [ ] T-006.1.07 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n79: - [ ] T-006.1.08 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes`\n80: - [ ] T-006.1.09 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n81: \n82: ### T-006.2: AgentRuntimeSpec\n83: \n84: - [ ] T-006.2.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeSpec struct`\n85: - [ ] T-006.2.02 字段 `Ports []TargetPort`（JSON tag: `targetPort,omitempty`）\n86: - [ ] T-006.2.03 字段 `Template *SandboxTemplate`（JSON tag: `podTemplate`，带 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记）\n87: - [ ] T-006.2.04 字段 `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration`（JSON tag: `sessionTimeout,omitempty`，带 `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` 标记）\n88: - [ ] T-006.2.05 字段 `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration`（JSON tag: `maxSessionDuration,omitempty`，带 `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` 标记）\n89: \n90: ### T-006.3: SandboxTemplate\n91: \n92: - [ ] T-006.3.01 定义 `type SandboxTemplate struct`\n93: - [ ] T-006.3.02 字段 `Labels map[string]string`（JSON tag: `labels,omitempty`）\n94: - [ ] T-006.3.03 字段 `Annotations map[string]string`（JSON tag: `annotations,omitempty`）\n95: - [ ] T-006.3.04 字段 `Spec corev1.PodSpec`（JSON tag: `spec`，带 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记）\n96: - [ ] T-006.3.05 导入 `corev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"`\n97: \n98: ### T-006.4: AgentRuntimeStatus\n99: \n100: - [ ] T-006.4.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeStatus struct`\n101: - [ ] T-006.4.02 字段 `Conditions []metav1.Condition`（JSON tag: `conditions,omitempty`，带 `+optional` 标记）\n102: \n103: ### T-006.5: AgentRuntimeList\n104: \n105: - [ ] T-006.5.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeList struct`，嵌入 `metav1.TypeMeta` 和 `metav1.ListMeta`\n106: - [ ] T-006.5.02 字段 `Items []AgentRuntime`（JSON tag: `items`）\n107: - [ ] T-006.5.03 添加标记 `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n108: - [ ] T-006.5.04 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n109: \n110: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；所有 kubebuilder 标记存在；GVK = `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=AgentRuntime`\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ## T-007: 创建 Scheme 注册 init() 函数\n115: \n116: - [ ] T-007.01 在 `agent_type.go` 或独立文件中添加 `func init()` 调用 `SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})`\n117: \n118: **验收**: `v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)` 成功将 `AgentRuntime` 和 `AgentRuntimeList` 注册到 `runtime.Scheme`\n119: \n120: ---\n121: \n122: ## T-008: 生成 DeepCopy 方法\n123: \n124: - [ ] T-008.01 运行 `make generate`（或 `controller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/...\" output:dir=./pkg/apis`）\n125: - [ ] T-008.02 验证 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 已生成在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 下\n126: - [ ] T-008.03 验证生成的 DeepCopy 方法覆盖 `AgentRuntime`、`AgentRuntimeSpec`、`AgentRuntimeStatus`、`AgentRuntimeList`、`SandboxTemplate`、`TargetPort`\n127: \n128: **验收**: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 存在；`go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n129: \n130: ---\n131: \n132: ## T-009: 编写单元测试 — Scheme 注册测试\n133: \n134: - [ ] T-009.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info_test.go`\n135: - [ ] T-009.02 测试 `AddToScheme(scheme)` 无错误\n136: - [ ] T-009.03 测试 `scheme.New(GVK)` 可识别 `AgentRuntime` 类型\n137: - [ ] T-009.04 测试 `scheme.New(GVKList)` 可识别 `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n138: \n139: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestSchemeRegistration -v` 通过\n140: \n141: ---\n142: \n143: ## T-010: 编写单元测试 — GVK/GVR 常量测试\n144: \n145: - [ ] T-010.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register_test.go`\n146: - [ ] T-010.02 测试 `GroupVersion.Group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`\n147: - [ ] T-010.03 测试 `GroupVersion.Version == \"v1alpha1\"`\n148: - [ ] T-010.04 测试 `AgentRuntimeKind == \"AgentRuntime\"`\n149: - [ ] T-010.05 测试 `AgentRuntimeListKind == \"AgentRuntimeList\"`\n150: - [ ] T-010.06 测试 `Resource(\"agentruntimes\")` 返回正确的 `GroupVersionResource`\n151: \n152: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestGroupVersionConstants -v` 通过\n153: \n154: ---\n155: \n156: ## T-011: 编写单元测试 — 默认值与零值测试\n157: \n158: - [ ] T-011.01 在 `agent_type_test.go` 中创建 `TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues`\n159: - [ ] T-011.02 验证 `SessionTimeout` 可为 nil（Go 零值）\n160: - [ ] T-011.03 验证 `MaxSessionDuration` 可为 nil（Go 零值）\n161: - [ ] T-011.04 验证 `Ports` 为空切片（Go 零值）\n162: - [ ] T-011.05 验证 `Template` 为必填字段（结构体可接受 nil，由 API Server 验证）\n163: \n164: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues -v` 通过\n165: \n166: ---\n167: \n168: ## T-012: 编写单元测试 — DeepCopy 测试\n169: \n170: - [ ] T-012.01 在 `agent_type_test.go` 中创建 `TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy`\n171: - [ ] T-012.02 构造包含嵌套字段（Ports、Template.Labels、Template.Spec.Containers、Conditions）的 `AgentRuntime` 实例\n172: - [ ] T-012.03 调用 `DeepCopy()` 获取副本\n173: - [ ] T-012.04 验证副本与原值相等\n174: - [ ] T-012.05 修改副本的 `Spec.Ports[0].Port`，验证原件不变（引用独立）\n175: - [ ] T-012.06 修改副本的 `Spec.Template.Labels[\"app\"]`，验证原件不变（map 引用独立）\n176: \n177: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy -v` 通过\n178: \n179: ---\n180: \n181: ## T-013: 编写单元测试 — ProtocolType 枚举测试\n182: \n183: - [ ] T-013.01 在 `codeinterpreter_types_test.go` 中创建 `TestProtocolTypeConstants`\n184: - [ ] T-013.02 验证 `ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`\n185: - [ ] T-013.03 验证 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS == \"HTTPS\"`\n186: \n187: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestProtocolTypeConstants -v` 通过\n188: \n189: ---\n190: \n191: ## T-014: 全量验证门禁\n192: \n193: - [ ] T-014.01 `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n194: - [ ] T-014.02 `go test ./pkg/apis/... -v` 全部通过\n195: - [ ] T-014.03 `go test ./pkg/apis/... -coverprofile=coverage.out` 覆盖率达标\n196: - [ ] T-014.04 `make generate` 成功且 `git diff --exit-code` 通过\n197: - [ ] T-014.05 所有 kubebuilder 标记验证（Required、default、Enum、subresource:status、printcolumn）\n198: \n199: **验收**: 全部检查项通过，AR-001 可标记为完成\n\n(End of file - total 199 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 任务清单\n\n> **Stage**: ST-4 (Implementation)\n> **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n> **Language**: Go\n> **Size**: S\n\n---\n\n## T-001: 创建 pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 目录结构\n\n- [ ] T-001.01 创建目录 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- [ ] T-001.02 确认 `go.mod` 中 `k8s.io/api`、`k8s.io/apimachinery`、`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` 依赖版本正确（v0.34.1 / v0.22.2）\n\n**验收**: 目录存在；`go mod tidy` 无报错\n\n---\n\n## T-002: 创建 doc.go — 包声明与代码生成标记\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775813774525,"end":1775813774531}}}}
